@baseUrl = {{baseUrl}}
@apiKey = {{apiKey}}
@jwt = {{login.response.body.accessToken}}

### Health (anonymous)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/health

# @name login
### Login (anonymous)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123!"
}

### Auth me (JWT)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Host metrics (API key required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/host/metrics
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Host servers (API key required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/host/servers
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Host metrics stream (API key required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/host/metrics/stream?intervalMs=2000
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
Accept: text/event-stream
